detaileddescription.para: Validates and saves the indoor climbing session to Firestore.

@component @description Form for logging indoor climbing sessions. Includes tracking for:
Climbing type (Boulder, Sport, Mixed)
Training details (Volume, Limit, etc.)
Grading (French/V-scale)
Detailed climb logging with attempts and styles
